    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are recorded as not-assessed, which is acceptable under the ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 framework for a Class II device with medium model influence. Quantitative hemolysis index predictions agree with FDA experimental benchmark within 15% across all operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 satisfies the regulatory acceptance criterion RH < 1.0. The assessment team concludes that sufficient credibility evidence has been assembled to support the intended use decision.",
